# 🧠 Second Brain AI Agent

A personal Jarvis-style AI agent that ingests your documents, remembers your conversations, learns your thinking style, and proactively surfaces relevant knowledge. Built on Claude (Anthropic), LangGraph, and Azure.

---

## Vision

An always-on personal intelligence system that:
- Ingests and understands documents, websites, videos, and structured data
- Remembers everything you discuss and updates its knowledge over time
- Learns your thinking style, preferences, and communication patterns
- Proactively surfaces relevant information without being asked
- Runs with full observability and traceability via LangSmith

---

## Core Principles

- Build incrementally — MVP first, expand in phases
- Every component observable from day one via LangSmith
- Claude (Anthropic) as primary reasoning model throughout
- Azure as cloud infrastructure backbone
- Simplicity over cleverness in early phases

